18#include "PDFBarcodeValue.h"
19
20namespace ZXing {
21namespace Pdf417 {
22
23/**
24* Add an occurrence of a value
25*/
26void
27BarcodeValue::setValue(int value)
28{
29 _values[value] += 1;
30}
31
32/**
33* Determines the maximum occurrence of a set value and returns all values which were set with this occurrence.
34* @return an array of int, containing the values with the highest occurrence, or null, if no value was set
35*/
36std::vector<int>
37BarcodeValue::value() const
38{
39 int maxConfidence = -1;
40 std::vector<int> result;
41 for (auto& entry : _values) {
42 if (entry.second > maxConfidence) {
43 maxConfidence = entry.second;
44 result.clear();
45 result.push_back(entry.first);
46 }
47 else if (entry.second == maxConfidence) {
48 result.push_back(entry.first);
49 }
50 }
51 return result;
52}
53
54int
55BarcodeValue::confidence(int value) const
56{
57 auto it = _values.find(value);
58 return it != _values.end() ? it->second : 0;
59}
60
61} // Pdf417
